Preconditions:
User is on the homepage: http://blazedemo.com/
Test Steps:
Locate the "Departure City" dropdown menu.
Select "Boston" from the "Departure City" dropdown.
Locate the "Destination City" dropdown menu.
Select "New York" from the "Destination City" dropdown.
Click on the "Find Flights" button.
Observe the results page.
Test Data:
Departure City: Boston
Destination City: New York
Expected Results:
Step 5:
User is redirected to the flights listing page.
Step 6:
A list of available flights from Boston to New York is displayed.
Each flight entry includes:
Airline Name
Flight Number
Departure Time
Arrival Time
Price
No error messages are displayed.
The URL reflects the search parameters (optional).